Write a program to find sum of an array elements using recursion.

Input & Output Format:

Input consists of one integer and one array.

First input consists of an size of an array and give the rest of the array elements.

Output consists of one integer.

Sample Input
5

1

2

3

4

5

Sample Output


Sum of an array is 15

//coding

#include<iostream>
using namespace std;
int sum(int n)
{
    int a[n],c=0,i;
    for(i=0;i<n;i++)
    {
        cin>>a[i];
        c=c+a[i];
    }
    cout<<"Sum of an array is "<<c;
}
int main()
{
    int n;
    cin>>n;
    sum(n);
}
